ISLAMABAD, Mar 10 (APP): Minister for Interior Sheikh Rashid Ahmad on Thursday urged all the voters and supporters of Prime Minister Imran Khan to gather in front of Parliament House at D-Chowk on the day of no-confidence motion.
In a tweet, he said ‘Insha’Allah’ they would offer thanksgiving prayer to Allah Almighty after the victory.
